{"type": "article", "id": 12990, "title": "磁悬浮滑板", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-04T12:17:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122456fF0H9Qd7hILO5JMu.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t相信很多人对在电影里面常常出现的悬浮滑板很感兴趣。这里 Lexus 将于明日发布磁悬浮滑板 “Hoverboards”，这款滑板底部设有悬浮引擎，可以在金属地板上悬浮起来，不过，这款滑板仍然没有驱动装置，需要外力才能浮起来，也就意味着，其实让它悬浮起来并不是一件轻松的事情。不过我们仍然可以期待一下，这是<a href=\"http://www.lexus-int.com/amazinginmotion/slide/\" target=\"_blank\">其官方网站</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140637yxQONj1AgurvE9MP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140638tFpNOvjI7lGMRr9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140639FkLVop8qQlTDAKMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140639ftUckM1Dl0qEdzP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}